{"id":1006958577,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"2Â months","timestamp":1690641378,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"9 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1006958577/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Reverse Vowels of a String","memory":"8 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    vector<char> vows = { 'a', 'e', 'i', 'o', 'u' , 'A', 'E', 'I', 'O', 'U' };\npublic:\n    string reverseVowels(string s) {\n        vector<char> vows_list;\n        for (auto i = 0; i < s.length(); i++)\n            if (find(vows.begin(), vows.end(), s[i]) != vows.end())\n                vows_list.push_back(s[i]);\n\n        int rev_idx = vows_list.size() - 1;\n        for (auto i = 0; i < s.length(); i++)\n            if (find(vows.begin(), vows.end(), s[i]) != vows.end())\n                s[i] = vows_list[rev_idx--];\n        return s;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"reverse-vowels-of-a-string","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
